title: CtrlPaint
description:
Ctrl+Paint the definitive collection of videos from the Website, made by me because of my disappointment with another torrent (the organization of files there was so atrocious, that I decided to redo it, then download the videos that were missing (for some great reason), then post this torrent).

This torrent is a lot of my frustration and effort to post a reliable source of those videos.

(P.S.: I took a few liberties in reorganizing the files, not much, but you'll see that some of the titles in CtrlPaint's videos (on Vimeo) don't really match the ones listed on their Library's webpage.)
